mrs. palfrey at the claremont is a 2005 us-produced comedy-drama film based on the 1971 novel by elizabeth taylor .   it was directed by dan ireland and produced by lee caplin , carl colpaert and zachary matz from a screenplay by ruth sacks caplin .   the film stars joan plowright and rupert friend , with zoe tapper , anna massey , robert lang , marcia warren , georgina hale , millicent martin , michael culkin and anna carteret .